snippet.title: Star86: First Contact
snippet.description:
STAR86 was a creative virtual world for kids that made exploring music like exploring space. It was closed on 31 July 2014.

Massive thanks to Play, Richic13, Adamm8, Fluffbug, Biggie, DrCheese, Partybot, Allis55, Travis36, Kim, WaffleGirl, Flex143, Skyler, Smash, Monkyt, Zakura, Umbreon, Dylanjmj, Roger, hotChick567, Saleh, KittyGirl123, Bluebird, Toodlepip and PlanetKing :)
